@startuml sd_DepartmentService_update
skinparam backgroundColor #F9FAFB
title DepartmentService.update(id, dto) - 更新部门

actor "调用方" as Client
participant "DepartmentController" as Ctrl
participant "DepartmentService" as Service
participant "DepartmentRepository" as Repo
participant "Department\n(实体)" as Entity

Client -> Ctrl: PUT /api/departments/{id}\n{name, code, parentId, ...}
Ctrl -> Service: update(id, dto)
Service -> Repo: findById(id)
Repo --> Service: 现有Department实体
note right of Service : 更新字段:\nsetName / setCode\nsetSortOrder\nsetParent(如提供)
alt parentId非空且非自身
  Service -> Repo: findById(parentId)
  Repo --> Service: 上级Department
  Service --> Entity: setParent(parent)
end
Service -> Repo: save(dept)
Repo --> Service: 更新后的Department
Service --> Ctrl: Department
Ctrl --> Client: ApiResponse<Department>
@enduml
